<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jura:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/88e62b65ed.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="scripts/jquery-min.js"></script>
    <script src="static/scripts/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="static/scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="static/scripts/script.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="static/css/bootstrap-min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="static/css/index.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="./icon.ico">
    <title>Athena - The Discord Bot</title>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('./components/navbar')  %> 

  <div onclick="window.location='/oauth/Login'" id="login_button" class="login_button">
    <a href="/oauth/login">LOGIN</a>
  </div>

  <noscript>
    <div class="warning_noscript">
      <h3>Warning!</h3>
      <p>You have to enable javascript to visit this page with full functionality.</p>
    </div>
  </noscript>

  <div class="cookie_warning">
    <p id="cookie_warn_text">üç™ We use cookies to ensure that we give the full functionality of our site. <a style="color: #7289DA; text-decoration: none;" href="/privacy">Learn more</a></p>
    <i id="cookie_warn_close" class="fas fa-times"></i>
  </div>

  <div class="short_description">
    <h3>A discord bot that can ful-fil your server needs...</h3>
    <p>Athena is a multi functional discord bot with fortnite stats, minecraft server information, weather forecast and much more!</p>
  </div>

  <div id="features" class="bot_features">
    <h3>Some Features of Athena</h3>
    <p>Here you can find some of Athena's interesting features.</p>
    <br/><br/>

    <div id="feature_1" class="feature">
      <h3 id="feature_title">Music</h3>
      <p id="feature_description">Athena has a powerful music module which you can listen music from spotify and youtube. Sssh little tip: You can set the volume as well :)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3 id="feature_title">Moderation</h3>
      <p id="feature_description">With Athena's big range of moderation commands you can moderate your sever easily and fastly!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3 id="feature_title">Fun</h3>
      <p id="feature_description">Do you like fun commands such as magik ? Cause we do and we put some fun commands to Athena that you may love!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3 id="feature_title">Misc</h3>
      <p id="feature_description">Other commands that we couldn't put in a section such as minecraft <strong>server information</strong> or <strong>weather forecast</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bot_features_end">
    <h1>Ready to try Athena ?</h1>
    <a id="bot_features_end_button" href="/invite" style="margin-top: 30px; background-color: #7289DA; border-color: #7289DA;" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" tabindex="-1" role="button" aria-disabled="true">Invite Athena!</a>
  </div>

  <%- include('./components/footer') %> 

  <% if (!userData) { %>
    <script> userNotLoggedIn(); </script>
  <% } else { %>
    <script> userLoggedIn(); </script>
  <% } %>
</body>
</html>
